<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>비자 신청 확인</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #003366, #0066cc);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 30px;
        }
        .application-details {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #007bff;
        }
        .detail-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            padding: 8px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }
        .detail-row:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .detail-label {
            color: #6c757d;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .detail-value {
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            padding: 6px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .next-steps {
            background-color: #e3f2fd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #2196f3;
        }
        .next-steps h3 {
            color: #1976d2;
            margin-top: 0;
        }
        .process-timeline {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .timeline-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .timeline-step {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            width: 30px;
            height: 30px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-right: 15px;
        }
        .timeline-content {
            flex: 1;
        }
        .timeline-title {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #333;
        }
        .timeline-desc {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #6c757d;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #6c757d;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .contact-info {
            margin-top: 15px;
            padding-top: 15px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #003366, #0066cc);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>✅ 비자 신청이 접수되었습니다</h1>
            <p>베트남비자24를 선택해 주셔서 감사합니다.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <p><strong>{{customerName}}</strong>님, 안녕하세요!</p>

            <p>베트남 비자 신청이 성공적으로 접수되었습니다. 전문가가 신청서를 검토하고 빠르게 처리해 드리겠습니다.</p>            <div class="application-details">
                <h3>📋 신청 정보</h3>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">신청 번호:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{applicationNumber}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">비자 종류:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{visaType}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">처리 유형:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{processingType}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">신청일:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{formatDate submittedAt}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">예상 처리 시간:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{estimatedProcessingTime}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="application-details">
                <h3>👤 신청자 정보</h3>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">성명:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{fullName}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">이메일:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{email}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">연락처:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{phone}}</span>
                </div>
                {{#if address}}
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">주소:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{address}}</span>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
                {{#if phoneOfFriend}}
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">현지 연락처:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{phoneOfFriend}}</span>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
            </div>

            <div class="application-details">
                <h3>✈️ 여행 정보</h3>
                {{#if entryDate}}
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">입국 예정일:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{formatDate entryDate}}</span>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
                {{#if entryPort}}
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">입국 공항:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{entryPort}}</span>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
                {{#if transitPeopleCount}}
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">경유 인원:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{transitPeopleCount}}명</span>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
                {{#if transitVehicleType}}
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">경유 차량 유형:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{transitVehicleType}}</span>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
            </div>            {{#if hasAdditionalServices}}
            <div class="application-details">
                <h3>🔧 추가 서비스</h3>
                {{#each additionalServices}}
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">•</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{this.name}}</span>
                </div>
                {{/each}}
            </div>
            {{/if}}

            {{#if pricing}}
            <div class="application-details">
                <h3>💰 비용 정보</h3>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">기본 비자 서비스:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{pricing.formatted.visaBasePrice}}</span>
                </div>
                {{#if pricing.visaVehiclePrice}}
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">경유 차량 비용:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{pricing.formatted.visaVehiclePrice}}</span>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
                {{#if pricing.additionalServicesPrice}}
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">추가 서비스 비용:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{pricing.formatted.additionalServicesPrice}}</span>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
                <div class="detail-row" style="border-top: 2px solid #007bff; padding-top: 10px; font-weight: bold;">
                    <span class="detail-label">총 결제금액:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value" style="color: #007bff; font-size: 18px;">{{pricing.formatted.totalPrice}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            {{else}}
            {{#if totalPrice}}
            <div class="application-details">
                <h3>💰 비용 정보</h3>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">총 비용:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{formatCurrency totalPrice currency}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            {{/if}}
            {{/if}}

            <div class="status-badge">접수 완료</div>

            <div class="next-steps">
                <h3>🚀 처리 절차</h3>
                <div class="process-timeline">
                    <div class="timeline-item">
                        <div class="timeline-step">1</div>
                        <div class="timeline-content">
                            <div class="timeline-title">신청서 검토</div>
                            <div class="timeline-desc">전문가가 제출된 서류와 정보를 검토합니다</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="timeline-item">
                        <div class="timeline-step">2</div>
                        <div class="timeline-content">
                            <div class="timeline-title">결제 처리</div>
                            <div class="timeline-desc">비자 신청 비용 결제를 진행합니다</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="timeline-item">
                        <div class="timeline-step">3</div>
                        <div class="timeline-content">
                            <div class="timeline-title">정부 기관 제출</div>
                            <div class="timeline-desc">베트남 이민청에 신청서를 제출합니다</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="timeline-item">
                        <div class="timeline-step">4</div>
                        <div class="timeline-content">
                            <div class="timeline-title">비자 발급</div>
                            <div class="timeline-desc">승인 완료 시 이메일로 비자를 발송합니다</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <h3>📱 진행 상황 확인</h3>
            <p>신청 번호 <strong>{{applicationNumber}}</strong>로 언제든지 진행 상황을 확인하실 수 있습니다.</p>

            <a href="{{trackingLink}}" class="button">🔍 신청 현황 조회</a>

            <h3>💡 유의사항</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>추가 서류가 필요한 경우 별도로 연락드립니다</li>
                <li>모든 진행 상황은 이메일과 SMS로 알려드립니다</li>
                <li>긴급한 문의사항은 고객센터로 연락해 주세요</li>
                <li>여권 유효기간이 6개월 이상 남아있는지 확인해 주세요</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <div class="contact-info">
                <strong>베트남비자24 고객센터</strong><br>
                📞 전화: 02-123-4567<br>
                📧 이메일: support@vietnamvisa24.com<br>
                💬 카카오톡: @vietnamvisa24<br>
                🌐 웹사이트: www.vietnamvisa24.com
            </div>

            <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #999;">
                본 메일은 발신전용 메일입니다. 문의사항은 고객센터로 연락 주세요.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
